text: Rostaing is a French leather company. Rostaing may also refer to: *Rostaing Berenguier (14th century), Provençal troubadour *Hubert Rostaing (1904–1999), French linguist *Charles Rostaing (1918–1990), French musician ==See also== *Rostagnus, for the given name Rostaing *House of Sabran, which had several members named Rostaing
title: Rostaing (disambiguation)
